{"tid":2456212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東男子不滿母親被罵 狂摑妻子23巴致其吐血","createTime":"2021-03-21T17:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T13:19:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ed6ee6aceacb28d802d756944cb5d0fe1c869b2b","tid":2456212,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"上近日廣傳一條家暴短片，丈夫被拍到在短短45秒內狂摑妻子逾23次，而妻子全程未有還擊或閃躲，結果慘被打至雙頰紅腫，其間甚至兩度吐血；不少網民狠批該名丈夫「渣男」，留言稱「世界上最廢的男人就是打女人和孩子的」。警方事後表示，事發原因仍有待了解。<br />\n<br />\n事發於廣東省梅州市五華縣，片段顯示該對夫妻當日坐在床邊，後面還有一名幼童，但丈夫完全不顧有孩子在旁，不斷狂摑妻子，每摑一下都傳出清脆的「啪啪」聲；妻子全程未有還擊或閃躲，最終被打至雙頰紅腫，其間甚至兩度吐血。<br />\n<br />\n有知情人士爆料稱，涉事丈夫因為妻子曾咒罵其母而動手，妻子又脾氣倔強，並揚言「你越打我越罵！」最後丈夫更質問：「有你這樣子做女人的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210322/T6CUOBW665BP7OCXZU63JDSUWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210322%2FT6CUOBW665BP7OCXZU63JDSUWI%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=72b1c290\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210322%2FT6CUOBW665BP7OCXZU63JDSUWI%2F&h=13aa08d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210322/T6CUOBW665BP7OCXZU63JDSUWI/</a>"},{"pid":"655ae87d8e7b3cd93317a9cc878fb62df5195002","tid":2456212,"uid":238370,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:29:26.000Z","msg":"陷家都係閪佬才<br />\n打和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead32e8f7bce1c537b3441c9df4dfecb2029331e","tid":2456212,"uid":365529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"片呢"},{"pid":"635c368a14d302a25a4a0679074b17d0be69fa6d","tid":2456212,"uid":86509,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T17:38:22.000Z","msg":"女權呢<br />\n搵日俾emma watson Brie Larson 睇"},{"pid":"5c7ac2641b086f4011b60056aaf71182d49c0ad5","tid":2456212,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"635c368a14d30